{"lastModified":1770640608936,"uri":"c::30662703947::vessel::fc5f7100-bc7a-11ef-a23b-0feec8e96c56","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nS/Y Kebisiks is a stunning 2025 Fountaine Pajot Aura 51 catamaran, epitomizing modern luxury and innovative design. Measuring 15.91m (50.8 ft) and accommodating up to 10 guests in 5 beautifully appointed cabins, including a spacious Maestro cabin with a queen-size bed and four double cabins, all with en-suite bathrooms, she promises an unforgettable charter experience. Her standout features include a voluminous layout, enhanced natural light, and seamless indoor-outdoor living, with fully retractable main bulkhead doors creating a breathtaking 3-meter opening between the saloon, galley, and cockpit. With a large flybridge, advanced energy management, full A/C, and a plethora of water toys, Kebisiks is perfectly equipped for both relaxation and adventure. Combined with a professional and attentive two-person crew, she offers an unrivaled platform for exploring the seas in style and comfort.\n\nPayment terms: 20%-30%-50%\n\nCancelation terms:\nCancellation up to 51 days before embarkation: 50% of the charter fee (deposit) retained\nCancellation within 30 days before embarkation: 100% of the charter fee retained\n\nRelocation fee in the Aegean Sea between islands 1000€ \n\nRelocation fee from Aegean to Ionian 1500€\n\nBank details:\nΒΕΤΑΚΑΠΠΑ ΝΕΠΑ \nGR11 0171 0410 0060 4116 2201 824\nBIC: PIRBGRAA\n","blueprint":{"name":"KEBISIKS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::fc5f7100-bc7a-11ef-a23b-0feec8e96c56::assets::5d4c08e0-bc7e-11ef-a8c3-f3c2479af11d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fc5f7100-bc7a-11ef-a23b-0feec8e96c56::assets::5d4b1e80-bc7e-11ef-a8c3-f3c2479af11d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fc5f7100-bc7a-11ef-a23b-0feec8e96c56::assets::5d6cd750-bc7e-11ef-a8c3-f3c2479af11d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fc5f7100-bc7a-11ef-a23b-0feec8e96c5